</P>
<P>
Update: AFGHAN-VIOLENCE. Taliban accused of using children as
human shields.
</P>
<P>
New: ISRAEL-RICE. Rice says U.S. will not "abandon the innocent
Palestinians in Gaza."
</P>
<P>
